            . I am a <rs id="t18220417-82-viclabel417" type="occupation">leather-cutter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-82-victim760 t18220417-82-viclabel417"></join>, and live in Fore-street, Cripplegate. On the 3d of April I was in <placeName id="t18220417-82-crimeloc418">Redcross-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18220417-82-crimeloc418" type="placeName" value="Redcross-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18220417-82-crimeloc418" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-82-off415 t18220417-82-crimeloc418"></join>, and felt something at my pocket; I missed my handkerchief, and upon turning round saw the prisoner and another lad close behind, and the handkerchief at his heels; he must have dropped it, it could have fallen from no other person; it was rather exposed - he appeared distressed.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-82-person762">
                  JAMES 
                  TUCKER
