                     <interp inst="t18220417-82-person762" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was coming along between nine and ten o'clock in the morning, and saw Curtis seize the prisoner, and saw the prisoner drop the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. - I throw myself on your mercy.</p>
